    "&Scoped-define AB_is_Running ~{~&UIB_is_Running~}" SKIP
    "&Scoped-define AppBuilder_is_Running ~{~&AB_is_Running~}" SKIP
    "&Scoped-define NEW            NEW" SKIP.

